# Copy this file to `cookie.env` (same folder) and paste your ScotlandsPeople
# session cookie. `cookie.env` is gitignored and must NEVER be committed.
#
# How to get the cookie:
#   1. Log in at https://www.scotlandspeople.gov.uk (free account).
#   2. Open DevTools (F12) > Application/Storage > Cookies > scotlandspeople.gov.uk
#   3. Find the cookie whose name starts with `SSESS...` and copy its name=value.
#
# The session expires (~1 month, or sooner on logout). If the fetch script reports
# a cookie/login error, log in again and refresh this value.

SP_COOKIE=SSESSxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx=PASTE_VALUE_HERE
